    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将成为咖啡馆的可爱主人并管理店铺。完成每个订单指定的小游戏即可完成料理。将完成的料理端给顾客，让顾客满意！如果不及时端上，顾客会因为等待而生气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>给顾客做料理并送上</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >店铺一开门，顾客就会接踵而至。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照订单制作并运送料理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075040/extras/0de0908d82fba77eedd2c952d912a345.avif?t=1737658047\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>丰富的料理菜单和迷你游戏</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要完成料理，需要通过各个迷你游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏进展，会不断有新菜单登场，敬请期待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075040/extras/689351631364a27f73e7cdbc693f24d8.avif?t=1737658047\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>扩大的店铺和增加的顾客</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顺利完成订单后，您的店铺会逐渐扩大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顾客数量也会增加，店铺会越来越忙碌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075040/extras/db6cc734a9110366c41f73e33b6a9d23.avif?t=1737658047\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>无限单人经营模式</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭载了耐久模式“Endless Mode”，您可以在其中竞赛看能单独经营多久。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确保不要弄错订单顺序，争取排名靠前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075040/extras/e46328b6bb3a990d20b1a418be7be378.avif?t=1737658047\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>协力经营模式</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭载了“2P Play Mode”，两人各自操作自己的角色并合作。合理分配角色，目标是无休营业100天！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075040/extras/03a236cd4895f88cb08e2f619ccf046f.avif?t=1737658047\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>配信指南</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是个人还是企业，无论是营利还是非营利，您均可在无需事先通知的情况下自由直播或发布本游戏的视频。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果可能的话，请在视频简介中附上Steam页面的链接。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于因直播或发布本游戏的视频而产生的任何损害，我们概不负责。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意，本指南的内容可能会在不另行通知的情况下进行更改。</p>",
